OL,4,CFTSE 100 slides amid fears of rising
OL,5,Cinflation
OL,6, The UK's benchmark share index, the
OL,7, FTSE 100, has tumbled more than 2% amid
OL,8, worries that inflation is set to rise.
OL,10,FIt follows similar falls in Asia and
OL,11,Fthe US as traders fear rising consumer
OL,12,Fprices will push up interest rates.
OL,14,FThe index has now retreated below the
OL,15,F7,000 mark to 6,980 after hitting a
OL,16,Fpost-pandemic high of 7,164 on Monday.
OL,18,F"The market just can't shake the
OL,19,Finflation fears which are clouding the
OL,20,Frecovery from Covid," said AJ Bell
OL,21,Finvestment director Russ Mould.
